list.abstract: 《Concentrate》是Xzibit演唱的英文歌曲，收录于专辑《Full Circle》中。

yingyinNormal.en: Like what? The o.j. in her mimosa was from concentrate, not fresh-squeezed?
yingyinNormal.zh: 比如？她的橙汁是浓缩的不是鲜榨的？

yingyinNormal.en: You're not telling anybody. Concentrate on something else. I can't.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你不要到处乱说。想想别的事儿。我做不到。

yingyinNormal.en: You know, I couldn't concentrate and I blushed every time he looked at me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我没办法专心上课，每次他看着我时我都会脸红。

yingyinNormal.en: I want you to concentrate on the passengers in your car. Get to know them.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要你留意同车厢的乘客，了解他们。

yingyinNormal.en: I told you, we're adding new operators all the time. Could we concentrate on my training?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们有加派接线员，专心训练，好吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Well, let's leave his credentials to one side for a moment and concentrate on what is important. Which is?
yingyinNormal.zh: 先不说他的资质，先说说重要的。那是什么？

yingyinNormal.en: And there are also some nice terrain features in this area-hills, small ridges, Mesas, and so forth, which help to concentrate the wind.
yingyinNormal.zh: 同时这里还有一些地形优势山丘，小山脊，台地等等这都有助于集风。

yingyinNormal.en: Claire, look, when I win the general, then we can concentrate on a Senate seat for you in Texas. You don't want to be in the House, anyway.
yingyinNormal.zh: 克莱尔，听我说，我赢下大选后，我们就可以专注于为你在德州赢得参议员席位。你反正也不会想待在众议院。

yingyinNormal.en: Don't give me that look. You were distracting me in front of the press. How am I supposed to concentrate with you yanking on my hair all the time?
yingyinNormal.zh: 别用那种眼神看我，是你把我推上报纸头版，你老是拉我的头发叫我怎么专心。
